Description:
    Installs Authlogic and Cancan with default configurations.
    Provide your own user fields, or just go with the boring defaults.
    The "magic" Authlogic fields will be added for you.

Example:
    rails generate authlogic:install
    rails generate authlogic:install email:string first_name:string last_name:string

    This will create:
        User scaffolding
        User sessions
        Password reset mechanism through email
        UserMailer with a pretty layout
        Login menu
        etc. (review it all before checking it in)

    You should then:
        Review create_users migration before running `rake db:migrate`
        Define authorization rules in ability.rb
